<p>We aim to reply to all complaints within 20 working days. If we cannot resolve your complaint we will tell you what steps you can take if you want your complaint to be further investigated.</p>

<p>We only deal with complaints relating to the service provided by the headquarters of the Ministry of Justice and its staff.</p>
